Definition: an inquisition set up in Italy in 1542 to curb the number of Protestants
Example: it was the Roman Inquisition that put Galileo on trial
Synonyms: Congregation_of_the_Inquisition, Inquisition, i, an, inquisition, set, up, in, Italy, to, curb, the, number, of, Protestants, it, was, Roman, that, put, Galileo, on, trial
Category: noun.group
